Content: so i bought my cbr as a non running bike got it running by a new battery and plugs it idled just fine revved just fine took it for a ride and rode amazing got it home parked it overnight went to ride it the next day it started with a misfire and then shut itself off and wouldn't start back up. so i instantly went to check the plugs when i pulled them they were as black as could be im a young mf so i have no idea where to start on carbed bikes the site wont let me post a picture of the plugs but just know they are black black all 4 of them
